{quote}You will need to download and install the latest production release of JIRA Server (for example, 'JIRA 6.0.2' at the time this document was written Please check https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/download for the latest version) and then move your data from your hosted JIRA Cloud site into your new JIRA Server site.{quote}

